#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/cpu-multicore.page:23
msgid ""
"The workload of running all of the programs on your computer is shared between "
"the processors. The more processors you have, the more the work can be shared "
"out. This reduces the load on each processor, which can help make the computer "
"run faster."
